Basic grammar for math word problems in English:

question : statements queries

statements : statements
           | statement
statement : subject VERB object PUNC
          | statement CONJUNCTION statement
subject : DETERMINER adjectives IDENTIFIER
        | adjectives IDENTIFIER
object : DETERMINER adjectives IDENTIFIER
       | adjectives IDENTIFIER

queries : queries
        | query
query : WHAT BE PROP DETERMINER adjectives IDENTIFIER
      | WHAT BE PROP adjectives IDENTIFIER
      | HOWMANY BE DETERMINER adjectives IDENTIFIER
      | HOWMANY BE adjectives IDENTIFIER

adjectives : adjectives
           | ADJECTIVE
           |
